headline: Five Cutting-Edge Startups Selected for Round Nine of GENIUS NY, the World's Largest Business Accelerator for Uncrewed Systems
summary: Empire State Development (ESD) this week announced the five teams selected to take part in round nine of the yearlong GENIUS NY business accelerator. The finalists were chosen from a highly competitive application process that received submissions from startups from around the world, including record interest from U.S. companies.
